r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">\"eccube-plugin\"</code><span> Tôi sẽ</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><span>yêu cầu: gói phụ thuộc</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span>Nếu có một gói được sử dụng bởi plugin, nó sẽ được nối thêm.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">\"ec-cube/plugin-installer\": \"~0.0.6\"</code><span> Hãy luôn luôn mô tả.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><span>phụ: thông tin phụ trợ</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">\"code\": \"[プラグインコード]\"</code><span> Hãy mô tả.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span>Một ví dụ về mô tả như sau.</span>\r\n<div class=\"language-yaml highlighter-rouge\">\r\n<div class=\"highlight\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code><span class=\"pi\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">name\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">ec-cube/ProductReview\"</span><span class=\"pi\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">version\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">1.0.0\"</span><span class=\"pi\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">description\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">商品レビュープラグイン\"</span><span class=\"pi\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">type\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">eccube-plugin\"</span><span class=\"pi\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">require\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"pi\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">ec-cube/plugin-installer\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">~0.0.6\"</span>\r\n    <span class=\"pi\">},</span>\r\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"s\">extra\"</span><span class=\"pi\">:</span> <span class=\"pi\"